1.Grafica basica ################################

Se genera grafia de lineas utilizando un color para cada continente

g_animada <- gapminder %>% 
  group_by(year, continent) %>% 
  summarize (mean_life = mean(lifeExp)) %>% 
  ggplot(aes (x = year, 
              y = mean_life,
              color = continent)) +
  geom_line()
## `summarise()` has grouped output by 'year'. You can override using the `.groups` argument.
g_animada

  1. Animando grafica ################################

Se anima la grfica

g_animada + transition_reveal(year)
